results.name: Number of partitions of n into distinct parts of order n.
comment: Order of partition is lcm of its parts.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..16384
formula: Coefficient of x^n in expansion of Sum_{i divides n} mu(n/i)*Product_{j divides i} (1+x^j).
program: (PARI) A074971(n) = { my(q=0); fordiv(n,i,my(p=1); fordiv(i,j,p *= (1 + 'x^j)); q += moebius(n/i)*p); polcoeff(q,n); }; \\ _Antti Karttunen_, Dec 19 2018
results.author: _Vladeta Jovovic_, Oct 05 2002
